《'''英倫玫瑰'''》（{{Lang-en|''The English Roses''}}），是一本由美國藝人[[麥當娜|瑪丹娜]]撰寫、傑彿瑞插圖的2003年兒童繪本，之後發展成兩位藝人的兒童繪本系列叢書。該書講述在倫敦的五個校園女生的生活和她們的問題<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.grimmpress.com.tw/gbooks_info.php?no=184|title=格林繪本網::英倫玫瑰|accessdate=2017-02-08|work=格林繪本網::英倫玫瑰|language=zh}}</ref>。

== 簡介 ==
《英倫玫瑰》講述夏洛蒂、愛咪、葛瑞絲、妮可四個女生的生活，她們四人嫉妒一個名叫娜娜的女孩。她們以為娜娜的人生很完美，因此而嫉妒她，但是娜娜很孤獨。娜娜的母親在她小時候去世，她和父親住在一間小房子裡，為了生活她需要煮飯打掃。娜娜沒有朋友，而她們這些英倫玫瑰認為娜娜很受歡迎、富裕、受寵，事實並非如此。

== 發展 ==
這是瑪丹娜的第一本童書。這本繪本於2003年9月15日由Callaway Editions出版社在全球100多個國家發行，並翻譯成30多種語言版本<ref>{{citation|title=Callaway press release for The English Roses|url=http://www.callaway.com/news_091503.htm|publisher=[[Callaway_Arts_&_Entertainment|Callaway Editions]]|accessdate=February 15, 2009|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20081211090610/http://www.callaway.com/news_091503.htm|archivedate=December 11, 2008}}</ref>。

== 續集 ==
2006年，瑪丹娜開始繼續撰寫英倫玫瑰系列叢書。另一本繪本《英倫玫瑰2：白馬王子來了》並非由傑彿瑞插圖，而是由史黛西插圖（該系列叢書裡的唯一一次例外）。首版精裝書於2006年10月24日由Callaway發行。五個女生的友誼在一個有魅力的新學生到來之後經受考驗<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.theguardian.com/books/2003/sep/21/booksforchildrenandteenagers.madonna|title=Observer review: The English Roses by Madonna | Books|accessdate=December 13, 2016|author=Kate Kellaway|date=September 21, 2003|work=The Guardian|archive-date=2017-05-10|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170510133903/https://www.theguardian.com/books/2003/sep/21/booksforchildrenandteenagers.madonna|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.sfgate.com/books/article/Madonna-s-kids-book-lands-with-a-thud-Million-2556902.php|title=Madonna's kids' book lands with a thud / Million copies of overblown, empty story|accessdate=December 13, 2016|author=Reviewed by David Kipen, Chronicle Book Critic|date=September 16, 2003|work=San Francisco Chronicle|archive-date=2016-03-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160305083419/http://www.sfgate.com/books/article/Madonna-s-kids-book-lands-with-a-thud-Million-2556902.php|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.people.com/people/article/0,,1074187,00.html|title=Madonna Writing Sequel to English Roses|accessdate=December 13, 2016|author=Stephen M. Silverman|date=June 20, 2005|work=People|archive-date=2016-03-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160304093320/http://www.people.com/people/article/0,,1074187,00.html|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.slate.com/articles/arts/books/2003/09/the_material_girl_gets_immaterial.html|title=Madonna's new children's book|accessdate=December 13, 2016|date=September 30, 2003|last=Shulman|first=Polly|work=Slate|archive-date=2017-08-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170809100651/http://www.slate.com/articles/arts/books/2003/09/the_material_girl_gets_immaterial.html|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.nytimes.com/2003/09/15/books/new-material-girl-madonna-a-mama-starts-writing-books-for-chi